      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HARA'S DOLLY (1) stalked the pace from a low draw last start and fought on well to finish 2 lengths away in third (22.09) at this track in a Grade 5 over 390m. One of the leading chances. TRIPPER ART (2) boasts a strong record this journey here with three wins and two minors from seven tries. Was out of the placings last time (19.90) at Capalaba in a Grade 5, finishing sixth and beaten 2.5 lengths. Makes strong appeal on best. SHE'S SAVVY (7) doesn't win out of turn but looks close to breaking through. Has hit the frame the last two runs, the latest when third (20.13) at this track. Goes very well here finding the frame in each of three starts. Racing well and deserves a win. SHIMA POLLY (8) form at this distance reads well.",
